00:02:27.030 --> 00:02:29.190 align:middle line:84%
in our dreams and
synchronicities,

00:02:29.190 --> 00:02:31.800 align:middle line:90%
he called this establishable.

00:02:31.800 --> 00:02:36.270 align:middle line:84%
Archetypes are the repeated
