00:03:19.420 --> 00:03:21.090 align:middle line:84%
It was this
adherence to symmetry

00:03:21.090 --> 00:03:23.040 align:middle line:84%
that gave Pauli
the insight needed

00:03:23.040 --> 00:03:25.740 align:middle line:84%
to formulate his
exclusion principle,

00:03:25.740 --> 00:03:28.500 align:middle line:84%
which became one of the
foundation stones of quantum

00:03:28.500 --> 00:03:32.820 align:middle line:84%
physics and won him the
Nobel Prize in 1945.

00:03:32.820 --> 00:03:35.580 align:middle line:84%
Today's physicists
have again returned

00:03:35.580 --> 00:03:38.400 align:middle line:84%
to this principle of
symmetry, as they now

