into our 3D world, parts of
its structure and activity

00:04:15.750 --> 00:04:18.190 align:middle line:90%
can be perceived and measured.

00:04:18.190 --> 00:04:21.540 align:middle line:84%
Bohm called our reality
of sensory experience

00:04:21.540 --> 00:04:23.670 align:middle line:90%
