00:05:27.630 --> 00:05:31.650 align:middle line:84%
the ways the archetypes
communicate to our psyche.

00:05:31.650 --> 00:05:36.480 align:middle line:84%
Pauli believed that mathematics,
physical processes, and quantum

00:05:36.480 --> 00:05:40.590 align:middle line:84%
probabilities must
also be archetypal.

00:05:40.590 --> 00:05:43.170 align:middle line:84%
And Jung agreed that
numbers, particularly

00:05:43.170 --> 00:05:46.080 align:middle line:84%
numbers one through
four, were the simplest

00:05:46.080 --> 00:05:49.920 align:middle line:84%
and most fundamental archetypes
