00:05:49.920 --> 00:05:52.620 align:middle line:90%
to both matter and psyche.

00:05:52.620 --> 00:05:55.350 align:middle line:84%
Through an active
imagination exercise,

00:05:55.350 --> 00:05:58.950 align:middle line:84%
Pauli once received an
epiphany about a key symbol

00:05:58.950 --> 00:06:01.980 align:middle line:84%
for the marriage of
matter and psyche.

00:06:01.980 --> 00:06:04.830 align:middle line:90%
That symbol is the i ring.

00:06:04.830 --> 00:06:06.480 align:middle line:90%
What is the i ring?

00:06:06.480 --> 00:06:09.780 align:middle line:84%
It is a mathematical
circle of unit radius

00:06:09.780 --> 00:06:14.280 align:middle line:84%
in the complex numbers plane
where the horizontal axis

00:06:14.280 --> 00:06:17.550 align:middle line:84%
consists of real numbers,
while the vertical axis is

00:06:17.550 --> 00:06:20.270 align:middle line:90%
imaginary numbers.

00:06:20.270 --> 00:06:23.930 align:middle line:84%
In mathematics, the symbol
i represents the square root

00:06:23.930 --> 00:06:28.550 align:middle line:84%
of minus 1, which is
nonsensical to the real world.

00:06:28.550 --> 00:06:31.710 align:middle line:84%
And thus, it is called
an imaginary number.

00:06:31.710 --> 00:06:33.560 align:middle line:84%
But even though
it has no meaning

00:06:33.560 --> 00:06:36.950 align:middle line:84%
in the real physical world,
mathematics and physics

00:06:36.950 --> 00:06:39.620 align:middle line:90%
would be incomplete without it.

00:06:39.620 --> 00:06:42.080 align:middle line:84%
The use of complex
numbers that contain

00:06:42.080 --> 00:06:47.840 align:middle line:84%
both real and imaginary numbers
is an integral part of science.

00:06:47.840 --> 00:06:52.070 align:middle line:84%
But this imaginary axis is
a mystery to scientists,

00:06:52.070 --> 00:06:55.340 align:middle line:84%
probably because they only
consider the real world

00:06:55.340 --> 00:06:56.900 align:middle line:90%
as the physical.

00:06:56.900 --> 00:07:00.920 align:middle line:84%
If the physical is but a
slice of the greater reality,

00:07:00.920 --> 00:07:05.540 align:middle line:84%
then perhaps these imaginary
numbers can serve as a bridge

00:07:05.540 --> 00:07:07.970 align:middle line:90%
to that greater reality.

00:07:07.970 --> 00:07:09.530 align:middle line:90%
How might that work?

00:07:09.530 --> 00:07:13.790 align:middle line:84%
Well, to answer that, let's
explore the i ring further.

00:07:13.790 --> 00:07:18.980 align:middle line:84%
For a complex number, a plus
ib that sits on this i ring,

00:07:18.980 --> 00:07:22.040 align:middle line:84%
there is an angle theta
that measures where

00:07:22.040 --> 00:07:24.180 align:middle line:90%
the number sits on the circle.

00:07:24.180 --> 00:07:26.480 align:middle line:84%
The formula that
expresses this circle

00:07:26.480 --> 00:07:31.700 align:middle line:84%
is known as Euler's formula,
e to the power i theta,

00:07:31.700 --> 00:07:34.700 align:middle line:84%
where e is the base
of natural logarithms

00:07:34.700 --> 00:07:40.010 align:middle line:90%
and has a value of about 2.718.

00:07:40.010 --> 00:07:43.910 align:middle line:84%
A case of this formula,
called Euler's identity,

00:07:43.910 --> 00:07:47.270 align:middle line:84%
occurs for theta
equals pi in radians,

00:07:47.270 --> 00:07:52.640 align:middle line:84%
pi being the famous 3.14 ratio
of a circle's circumference

00:07:52.640 --> 00:07:54.330 align:middle line:90%
to its diameter.

00:07:54.330 --> 00:07:56.510 align:middle line:84%
For Euler's identity,
the relation

00:07:56.510 --> 00:08:01.796 align:middle line:84%
becomes e to the power
i pi equals minus 1.

00:08:01.796 --> 00:08:03.950 align:middle line:84%
This Euler's identity
is considered

00:08:03.950 --> 00:08:08.300 align:middle line:84%
to be an example of supreme
mathematical beauty,

00:08:08.300 --> 00:08:10.940 align:middle line:84%
because it shows a profound
connection between some

00:08:10.940 --> 00:08:15.214 align:middle line:84%
of the most fundamental numbers
in mathematics, namely e, i,

00:08:15.214 --> 00:08:16.870 align:middle line:90%
and pi.

00:08:16.870 --> 00:08:19.820 align:middle line:84%
A relation could
even be extended

00:08:19.820 --> 00:08:22.820 align:middle line:84%
to include the
golden ratio of phi,

00:08:22.820 --> 00:08:25.850 align:middle line:84%
giving an even more
profound connection to how

00:08:25.850 --> 00:08:28.610 align:middle line:84%
these numbers and
Euler's formula

00:08:28.610 --> 00:08:31.760 align:middle line:84%
all relate to
nature's golden mean.

00:08:31.760 --> 00:08:37.549 align:middle line:84%
Each of these numbers, e, phi,
pi, and the square root of 5

00:08:37.549 --> 00:08:40.280 align:middle line:84%
are all called
transcendental numbers,

00:08:40.280 --> 00:08:46.580 align:middle line:84%
because they transcend the
power of algebraic methods.

00:08:46.580 --> 00:08:49.400 align:middle line:84%
Why should we care
about this. i ring?

00:08:49.400 --> 00:08:51.420 align:middle line:90%
How does it relate to us?

00:08:51.420 --> 00:08:53.540 align:middle line:84%
Again, Pauli was
shown this ironing

00:08:53.540 --> 00:08:57.380 align:middle line:84%
