00:35:51.646 --> 00:36:13.410 align:middle line:90%


00:36:13.410 --> 00:36:17.160 align:middle line:84%
It is much like the North
Star that ancient explorers

00:36:17.160 --> 00:36:18.990 align:middle line:90%
used for navigating.

00:36:18.990 --> 00:36:21.900 align:middle line:84%
As the Earth rotates,
the stars in the sky

00:36:21.900 --> 00:36:25.650 align:middle line:84%
trace out many concentric
circles, with the North Star

00:36:25.650 --> 00:36:27.390 align:middle line:90%
as the center.

00:36:27.390 --> 00:36:31.170 align:middle line:84%
This is very similar to the
ancient kabbalistic depiction

00:36:31.170 --> 00:36:33.600 align:middle line:84%
of the 10 spherot
when they originally

00:36:33.600 --> 00:36:35.445 align:middle line:90%
emanated out from the Ein Sof.

00:36:35.445 --> 00:36:38.840 align:middle line:90%


00:36:38.840 --> 00:36:40.610 align:middle line:84%
Throughout this
episode, we've talked

00:36:40.610 --> 00:36:42.800 align:middle line:84%
about different
ways of exploring

00:36:42.800 --> 00:36:46.580 align:middle line:84%
the nature of consciousness
beyond the hologram

00:36:46.580 --> 00:36:49.970 align:middle line:84%
into the implicate order,
the undivided wholeness

00:36:49.970 --> 00:36:53.840 align:middle line:84%
or imaginary nature, the
greater realm where spirit

00:36:53.840 --> 00:36:56.780 align:middle line:90%
and matter unite and are one.

00:36:56.780 --> 00:36:59.720 align:middle line:84%
And we've explored
ways to access

00:36:59.720 --> 00:37:04.360 align:middle line:84%
the center, the divine
spark of our eternal being.

00:37:04.360 --> 00:37:08.920 align:middle line:84%
What might the substance
of this eternal realm be?

00:37:08.920 --> 00:37:11.800 align:middle line:84%
Carl Jung said it
was the archetypes.

00:37:11.800 --> 00:37:14.890 align:middle line:84%
But he also said that
the archetypes are just

00:37:14.890 --> 00:37:18.550 align:middle line:90%
aspects of the one self.

00:37:18.550 --> 00:37:22.990 align:middle line:84%
Similarly, in kabbalah,
the one source, Ein Sof,

00:37:22.990 --> 00:37:27.340 align:middle line:84%
sends out 144,000
rays from itself.

00:37:27.340 --> 00:37:31.120 align:middle line:84%
Each of these raised could
be called an archetype.

00:37:31.120 --> 00:37:33.100 align:middle line:84%
But they are much
more than that.

00:37:33.100 --> 00:37:35.380 align:middle line:90%
They are forces of creation.

00:37:35.380 --> 00:37:39.150 align:middle line:84%
They bring order as
well as diversity

00:37:39.150 --> 00:37:41.500 align:middle line:84%
so that the
magnificence of the one

00:37:41.500 --> 00:37:44.380 align:middle line:84%
can be expressed
through the many,

00:37:44.380 --> 00:37:48.970 align:middle line:84%
thereby coming to know itself
and its infinite potential.

00:37:48.970 --> 00:37:55.210 align:middle line:84%
This one, the substance of the
eternal realm, is divine will.

00:37:55.210 --> 00:37:59.830 align:middle line:84%
We can also call it light,
love, spirit, intelligence,

00:37:59.830 --> 00:38:03.700 align:middle line:84%
pure awareness, or
the celestial fire.

00:38:03.700 --> 00:38:08.980 align:middle line:84%
This divine will is universal,
eternal, and infinite.

00:38:08.980 --> 00:38:13.660 align:middle line:84%
It is unity experienced through
its multiple expressions

00:38:13.660 --> 00:38:16.150 align:middle line:90%
in the world, through us.

00:38:16.150 --> 00:38:19.120 align:middle line:84%
As this will flows
through us, it

00:38:19.120 --> 00:38:23.110 align:middle line:84%
is manifested in different
ways, because our way

00:38:23.110 --> 00:38:26.210 align:middle line:90%
of relating to it is unique.

00:38:26.210 --> 00:38:28.870 align:middle line:90%
We are each a unique expression.

00:38:28.870 --> 00:38:32.950 align:middle line:84%
But only when our soul is
aligned with our spirit

00:38:32.950 --> 00:38:35.530 align:middle line:84%
and balanced in
the middle pillar

00:38:35.530 --> 00:38:39.610 align:middle line:84%
do we truly flow this
will in a pure way.

00:38:39.610 --> 00:38:41.560 align:middle line:84%
Our imbalances or
blocks to the light

00:38:41.560 --> 00:38:45.430 align:middle line:84%
can distort the expression
of our divinity.

00:38:45.430 --> 00:38:48.580 align:middle line:84%
Thus we must seek
to purify our soul,

00:38:48.580 --> 00:38:51.190 align:middle line:84%
attain higher levels
of consciousness,

00:38:51.190 --> 00:38:55.840 align:middle line:84%
and increase awareness of
our multi-dimensionality.

00:38:55.840 --> 00:38:59.890 align:middle line:84%
As we do, we heal, we
transform and progress.

00:38:59.890 --> 00:39:03.080 align:middle line:90%


00:39:03.080 --> 00:39:06.980 align:middle line:84%
By strengthening our ability
to align with that will

00:39:06.980 --> 00:39:10.400 align:middle line:84%
and by mastering the way
we apply in our life,

00:39:10.400 --> 00:39:13.370 align:middle line:84%
we then stand in the
center and direct

00:39:13.370 --> 00:39:15.860 align:middle line:90%
the forces of transformation.

00:39:15.860 --> 00:39:18.860 align:middle line:84%
The divine spark,
once we connect to it,

00:39:18.860 --> 00:39:22.360 align:middle line:90%
is directed by will alone.

